{
    "text": "Less than an hour north of Rome lies Calcata, a medieval village clinging to a volcanic cliff surrounded by the densely-wooded Treja valley.   With its rugged tufa walls and steep pathways, entering this mystical, car-free hamlet it\u2019s like stepping back in time or falling into a dream where Woodstock meets Hansel and Gretel. \u2764\ud83d\udc9a\ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf9 \ud83c\udfa5 Video by @gianluigi.palomba   #visititaly #italy #italia #lazio #calcata #italian_trips #rome #italyescapes #lonelyplanet #natgeo #natgeotravel #culturetrip #travellingthroughtheworld #guardiancities #passionpassport #bbctravel #cnntravel",
